  "body": "Originally posted by @ryanreich as https://github.com/ethereum/webthree-umbrella/issues/682 and moved here.\n\nA file such as \n\n```\nimport \"../File.sol\";\n```\n\nwill raise the `solc` error\n\n```\n<stdin>:1:1: Error: Source \"File.sol\" not found: File not found.\nimport \"../File.sol\";\n^-------------------^\n```\n\nwhether or not `../File.sol` actually exists.\n",
